"    Longitudinal standards for height and pubertal development in boys. The units for penis stage and pubic hair growth range from 2+ to 5+ and for testes volume from 4 mL to 12 mL. Each tick on the lines of pubertal development represents a percentile ranging from 97th to the 3rd percentile.",
